FormAction.Description: When Please select option is selected in process text box clearing the process details

Parameter.subfield: Upgrader has been scheduled. You can view results in audit log

FormVariable.Value: This utility will update the jobs for the selected business process to use the latest released version. Changes to the layout of the business process may result in unpredictable results, For example it may not be possible to have the current set of live activities for a job in the latest version. Before proceeding, ensure your main TotalAgility database is backed up. Do you want to continue?
